接待医疗队、隔离疑似病例  这些酒店扛得很艰难。
Hosting medical teams, quarantining suspected cases These hotels are having a tough time.
张雅楠2020-02-05 15:52。
Nan Zhang 2020-02-05 15: 52.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 张雅楠1月27日，程立向区政府提出，他旗下的武汉市四季鑫宝来酒店可以无偿接待援汉医疗队，第二天，他迎来了浙江省第二批医疗队的入驻。
Zhang Yanan, a reporter for the Economic Observation Network, told local authorities on January 27 that his hotel, the Four Seasons Xin Borai Hotel in Wuhan, could receive medical aid teams free of charge.
。
.
149人的医疗团队，来自浙江省11个地市各级医院的呼吸科、感染科、院感科、重症医学科、检验科等科室，至今已在天佑医院展开医疗救治多日。
The 149-member medical team from the respiratory, infectious, sensory, severe and laboratory departments of 11 local hospitals in Zhejiang Province has been conducting medical treatment in Tianyou Hospital for many days.
。
.
鑫宝来酒店距离天佑医院约500米，步行8分钟，对通勤来说，这是个挺有幸福感的距离，医疗队估计，还将在此战斗至少一个月。
About 500 meters from Tianyou Hospital and eight minutes' walk, Xin Bao Lai Hotel is a blissful distance to commute, and the medical team estimates there will be at least another month of fighting.
。
.
一个月，其实远超程立的预期，他曾乐观估计一周，最多十天半个月，疫情就可以得到控制，酒店可以慢慢走上正轨，然而，现实比他预想的要严峻得多。
For a month, he was optimistic that a week, or at most a half-month at most, would bring the outbreak under control and the hotel back on track, but the reality was much tougher than he had expected.
。
.
程立介绍，鑫宝来酒店是一家四星级标准的高端商务酒店，平均每个月包括房租、水电、人工在内的运营成本在250万元左右。
Cheng Li, Xin Bao Lai Hotel is a four-star standard high-end business hotel, the average monthly operating costs including rent, utilities, labor and about 2.5 million yuan.
。
.
目前除上述固定的运营成本之外，鑫宝来酒店为医护团队提供了60元/餐标准的三餐外加宵夜，这是一个不低的生活标准，整体餐饮费用在3万元/天，一个月是90万元。
In addition to the above-mentioned fixed operating costs, Xin Bao Lai Hotel provides the medical team with 60 yuan / meal standard three meals plus supper, which is not a low standard of living. The total cost of the meal is 30,000 yuan per day and 900,000 yuan per month.
。
.
对任何一家酒店来说，这都是无法忽略的压力。
For any hotel, this is a pressure that cannot be ignored.
。
.
和政府方面的沟通一直在进行，包括街道、区政府和商务局，程立得到消息是，最后会有补贴，谁来给，什么标准，现在还不知道。
Communication with the government has been ongoing, including with street, district and business authorities, and Cheng has been told that there will eventually be subsidies, who will give and what standards.
。
.
2月4日，来自民间的支援先到了。
On 4 February, support from the civil society arrived first.
。
.
经济观察网获悉，由阿里巴巴13位女性合伙人成立的湖畔魔豆公益基金会确定，在2月，为鑫宝来酒店提供50万元资助。
The Economic Watch Network has learned that the Lakeside Magic Bean Foundation, founded by 13 Alibaba women partners, will provide $500,000 in February for the Xin Pao Lai Hotel.
。
.
50万元能缓解多少压力呢？程立说，够买菜的了。
How much pressure can 500, 000 yuan relieve? Cheng said, enough to buy vegetables.
。
.
买菜，确实符合湖畔魔豆公益基金会这一资助的方向，2月2日，湖畔魔豆公益基金捐赠1000万元成立“湖畔魔豆抗疫项目转型资金”，用于解决疫情定点医院相关医护人员以及家属的餐饮及生活保障问题。
On February 2, the Lakeside Magic Bean Foundation donated 10 million yuan to set up a fund for the transformation of the Lakeside Magic Bean Anti-epidemic Project.
。
.
这笔资助，离不开浙江医疗队的牵线，酒店和基金会取得联系后，湖畔魔豆基金会对接待标准、医疗人员的吃用等一一审核，确定了上述捐助。
The donation, which could not be made without the help of Zhejiang Medical Team, was confirmed after the hotel and the foundation contacted, and the Lakeside Magic Bean Foundation examined the standards of reception and the use of medical personnel.
。
.
程立在医护人员群里，知道医护人员每天的工作量有多大、有多辛苦。
Cheng stands among the medical staff and knows how much work and how much work they do every day.
。
.
因为防护服紧缺，医护人员不论男女都会穿上纸尿裤，特别口渴才敢喝一点水，这都是为了减少上厕所的几率，节约防护服。
Because of the shortage of protective clothing, medical personnel, both men and women, will wear diapers, especially thirsty before drinking a little water, all to reduce the chance of going to the toilet and save on protective clothing.
。
.
其实鑫宝来酒店同样面临难题，除了上述成本问题外，满员约170人的工作团队，现在只有约70人能够到岗，客房部只有5个人。
In fact, Xin Bao Lai hotel also faces difficulties, in addition to the above-mentioned cost issues, the full staff of about 170 staff, can now only about 70 people can be posted, the Housekeeping Department only five people.
。
.
出于安全和人力两方面的考虑，双方同意，酒店工作人员不进入医护人员房间服务。
For security and manpower reasons, the two sides agreed that the hotel staff would not enter the medical staff room service.
毛巾、床品、三餐等都统一放在楼道，医护人员需要时自助。
Towels, bedding, meals and so on are uniformly placed in the corridor, medical personnel need to help themselves.
。
.
现实中满是难处，但双方收获的是体谅和肯定。
Reality is full of difficulties, but both sides gain understanding and affirmation.
。
.
程立说，医护人员没有任何怨言，他们说，有什么做什么，做什么吃什么。
'Medical staff have no complaints, 'Mr. Cheng said.' They say they do what they do and eat what they eat. '
。
.
不仅如此，医疗队为感谢酒店的支持，集体捐了1万元，请程立犒劳工作人员；一位ICU的护士，个人向酒店捐了6600元，感谢酒店提供的无偿服务和工作人员顶着巨大压力的付出。
In addition, the medical team thanked the hotel for its support with a donation of 10,000 yuan, asking Cheng to reward the staff. An ICU nurse donated 6,600 yuan to the hotel.
。
.
像程立一样为抗疫付出的酒店业人士还有很多，周超就是其中一位。
Like Cheng Li paid for the fight against the epidemic hotel industry there are many, Zhou Chao is one of them.
。
.
与程立不同，周超旗下的酒店品牌，被征用了两家店，每家提供约90间客房，用于隔离疑似病例。
Unlike Cheng, Zhou Chao's hotel brand has been expropriated from two stores, each offering about 90 rooms for quarantine of suspected cases.
。
.
公开信息显示，按照武汉市防控指挥部要求，武汉实行发热市民分级分类就医，江岸区、汉阳区、硚口区等武汉市各个城区陆续安排集中隔离观察点，自1月29日起，不少酒店被相关城区征用，上述酒店就是其中的2家。
Since January 29, many hotels have been requisitioned by the relevant urban areas, including Wuhan, Hanyang District, Zhangkou District and other urban areas of Wuhan City.
。
.
周超介绍，酒店内部做了隔离，为医护人员设置了专门的通道，房间、卫生间需要根据防疫部门的指导，由工程部人员穿着全套防护服进行日常消毒。
Zhou Chao introduced that the hotel has done isolation, for the medical staff set up a special passageway, rooms, bathrooms according to the guidance of the epidemic prevention department, engineering personnel wearing full protective clothing for routine disinfection.
周超也从28日开始，24小时不离酒店，准备随时响应。
Zhou Chao also began on the 28th, 24 hours away from the hotel, ready to respond at any time.
。
.
目前，随着火神山医院投入使用、洪山体育馆临时改建为方舱医院即将投入使用，上述两家酒店没有入住新的疑似病例人员，隔离何时结束，需等政府通知。
At present, with the opening of the Mount Huo Hospital and the temporary conversion of the Hongshan Stadium into a new cabin hospital, no new suspected cases are being accommodated at the two hotels. The end of the isolation will be subject to notification by the Government.
。
.
对于目前面临的经济压力，周超没有提供详细数据，只表示，如果要核算经济成本，肯定是严重的亏损。
Zhou did not provide detailed figures on the economic pressures facing him, saying only that if the economic costs were to be accounted for, it would be a serious loss.
。
.
当记者再次追问时，周超说，你所提的问题，其实是我们的酒店做了隔离酒店之后，没有顾客敢住了，这个问题现在由不得我们考虑那么多，我们面对的是没有硝烟的战争，只有把这个灾难战胜了，我们才有光明的那一天。
When asked again by reporters, Zhou Chao said that the question you raised is that our hotel has been a secluded hotel, no one dared to stay, this issue is not considered so much, we are faced with a war without smoke, only to overcome this disaster, we have a bright day.
。
.
对于补偿，周超称，政府表示会减免税收，会和酒店业主沟通协商减免一个月的房租。
As for compensation, Zhou said the government said it would waive taxes and negotiate a one-month rent reduction with hotel owners.
。
.
面临巨大的经营压力，不论是程立还是周超，在接受经济观察网采访时，说了同样一句话：天下兴亡，匹夫有责。
Faced with enormous operational pressure, whether Cheng or Zhou Chao, in an interview with the Economic Watch network, said the same words: the world rises and falls, the husband is responsible.
。
.
知名公益律师、北京市致诚律师事务所律师何国科介绍，《中华人民共和国民法总则》第一百一十七条规定，为了公共利益的需要，依照法律规定的权限和程序征收、征用不动产或者动产的，应当给予公平、合理的补偿。
Article 117 of the General Civil Law of the People's Republic of China stipulates that, where immovable or movable property is requisitioned or requisitioned according to the limits of authority and procedures prescribed by law for reasons of public interest, fair and reasonable compensation shall be given.
。
.
他呼吁，不要把责任都压给民营酒店，可以让酒店提供服务，湖北省当地政府、红十字会、慈善总会等机构应该给予资金的支持。
He called for funds from local governments, Red Cross and charitable associations in Hubei province, instead of putting the blame on private hotels.
。
.
记者致电武汉市卫健委和武汉市市长热线了解相关征收补偿方案，截至发稿时，未获回复。
The reporter called Wuhan Health Commission and Wuhan City Mayor's Hotline to understand the relevant levy compensation scheme, as of the time of writing, no response.
。
.
